+ We've made significant progress in moving to BPM (BOSH Process Manager). This
is a significant departure from how jobs are launched

+ We've configured new MySQL properties to improve performance of Galera plans

+ Bumped the Percona Server version to v5.7.24-26

+ Bumped the Golang version to 1.12.x

### Resolved Issues

+ Resolved an issue which enables Java applications to use Galera plans, with or without enabling TLS

+ Resolved issue with the internal diagnostic and backup components of Galera plans to make troubleshooting easier and more accurate

+ Resolved an issue so that the drain script no longer times out

